The issues service will currently post the message as follows:

{{{\\
Changeset rX:deadbeef20d285 :

{code}
Some message.
Fixes BCLOUD-21
{code}

}}}

Instead, it would read better if the changset line was identical to the one seen in the history view, and was after the commit message, rather than above it.

Example: http://bitbucket.org/prencher/wtforms/history/LICENSE.txt
